{"tid":417802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"談台獨讓中國氣噗噗 中國官媒：先把賴清德的頭打出兩個包","createTime":"2017-09-29T04:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T06:36:37.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1252037088e639c5119ce51526d023253c1c0b12","tid":417802,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"談台獨讓中國氣噗噗 中官媒：先把賴清德的頭打出兩個包<br />\n<br />\n2017-09-28 11:19<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕行政院長賴清德日前的台獨說，引起中國強烈回應，昨國台辦嗆聲：「台灣從來不是一個國家，也永遠不可能成為國家」，今（28日）中共官媒環球時報再發文嗆聲，揚言要把賴清德的頭打出兩個包。<br />\n<br />\n中共官媒《環球時報》表示，賴清德是第一個公開表示支持台獨的行政院長，之前行政院長中無一人敢這樣踩紅線，認為賴清德言論提高了對中國尋釁滋事的級別，如果中國不作出強有力反應，會引發其他台灣政客仿效，強調要「先把賴清德的頭打出兩個包」，通過政治、經濟、外交手段來懲治台灣，證明中國隨時可以徹底摧毀台獨勢力。<br />\n<br />\n最後還警告台灣，有《反分裂國家法》在等著他們，「如果他們真的活夠了，那麼那部大法將不是棍棒，而是一把利刃。」<br />\n<br />\n昨上午中國國台辦發言人馬曉光表示，中國和台灣同屬一個中國，台灣從不是一個國家，也永遠不可能成為一個國家；賴清德則反駁，台灣是一個國家，這是一個事實，國家名稱是中華民國。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2206919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2206919&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6ffbe8ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2206919&h=39e9cae4\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2206919</a>"},{"pid":"ecc9042b4d24d7f86d2076e9b21cf3190cdd8204","tid":417802,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"胡語&quot;打出2個包&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc92719760173303341a392b7859d9cff8244ea","tid":417802,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"80f21ea9a0fed445a05daa87e09d30d649dc75fc","tid":417802,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"習包包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7151cb25840978e817a2d5dad0316f8ff2765c64","tid":417802,"uid":4493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"支那人特別野蠻暴力"},{"pid":"a6461f9818689d42c3c084fac279d61e9d9dd2ae","tid":417802,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紙老虎"},{"pid":"9cdcbdba73adab172351c865db54556b5737c73f","tid":417802,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那人特別野蠻暴力</blockquote><br />\n但支那人日日話自己好和平，真是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d142a1ab064a64db93a87d52cbc58967559e1127","tid":417802,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"流氓政權先會咁講嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有個咩反分裂國家法，咁仲唔派人過去拉人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}